t-failure-resources/glossary">Glossary</a></li></ul></li><li class="first-level-link hide-for-large"><a href="/sitemap">Sitemap</a></li></ul></nav></div></div></header><main class="patient"><section class="hero"><div id="main" tabindex="-1" class="hero-image-wrapper"><div class="row"><div class="large-5 large-push-7"><div class="tagline show-for-medium"><p>He always took his dad's advice to heart</p><h2>Heart failure took that wisdom away</h2></div><div id="main-mobile" class="ctas"><div class="row"><a href="/about-bidil/clinical-trial-results"><div class="cta"><div class="left-side"><p>BiDil Impact</p></div><div class="right-side show-for-large"><p class="greater-than">&gt;</p></div></div></a><a href="/patient-savings-support"><div class="cta"><div class="left-side"><p>BiDil Savings</p></div><div class="right-side show-for-large"><p class="greater-than">&gt;</p></div></div></a></div></div></div></div></div></section><h1 class="sr-only">BiDil (isosorbide dinitrate/hydralazine HCl) | Heart Failure Medication</h1><section id="home-patient" class="main-section"><section id="main-content" class="main-content"><section id="gray-background"><div class="row"><div class="content medium-6 small-12 columns"><h2>Heart failure steals precious moments away.</h2><p><a href="/about-heart-failure">Heart failure (HF) is a big problem, especially for African Americans.</a> If you’re African American, you’re more likely than people in other ethnic groups to get HF at a younger age, and you’re more likely than others to be hospitalized.<sup>1</sup> Unfortunately, African Americans are also more likely to die earlier than are other people with HF.<sup>2</sup></p><p>BiDil is the only heart failure medicine specifically indicated for self-identified African American patients.</p></div><div class="content medium-5 small-12 columns video-container"><a data-open="exampleModal1" class="linkVideo"><img src="/images/video_thumbnail.png" alt="See Renil's Heart Failure Story"></a><a href="/pdf/Bidil_Renil_s_Heart_Failure_Story_Transcript.pdf?v=1714849095045" target="_blank" class="bold green-link">View Transcript</a><br><br><h3 class="p bold">IMPORTANT SAFETY INFORMATION</h3><p>Headache and dizziness were the most frequent side effects experienced in studies with BiDil.</p><a href="#isi" class="bold green-link">Please click here to see full  Important Safety Information for BiDil.</a><div id="exampleModal1" data-reveal="" role="dialog" aria-modal="true" aria-labelledby="modal-title" class="large reveal"><section><h2 id="modal-title">Renil’s Heart Failure Story</h2><div class="row"><div class="small-12 columns"><div class="iframe-container"><div id="player"></div></div><button data-close="" aria-label="Close modal" type="button" class="close-button first-focusable-element"><span aria-hidden="true">×</span></button></div></div></section><script>var dialog = document.querySelector('[role="dialog"]');
